I can probably explain it, atleast the way i understand it, the reason so many contain this weird made-up or silly additions it a parody/satire of literally any SCP that has to make up a new task-force, Operation, Project, Cognihazard, or security classification. There's a lot of them, and everyone feels like theirs has to be unique, so you end up with a lot of authors just vomiting letters together and hoping the words it makes doesnt seem too weird, just weird enough. Read enough of Project Montauks, Level Ghelidus-GHK authorization, ect. and it starts getting humorous. Thus, where comedy can exist, it is created, thus this long-running clique is constantly mocked here and in other -J's.







